      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "This release moves the manual sync control to the status bar and keeps your screen awake during sync on mobile.\n\n## Added\n\n- **Your screen stays awake during sync on mobile.** Air Sync now holds a screen wake lock while a sync is running, so a large or slow sync finishes instead of stalling when the screen would otherwise turn off.\n\n## Changed\n\n- **Manual sync moved to the status bar.** \"Sync now\" and the live sync status now sit together in the status bar instead of the ribbon. The `Air Sync: Sync now` command is unchanged.",
